riants of CommonsenseQA, Social IQa, and Novel Concept Reasoning benchmarks, demonstrating superior performance in generating diverse, accurate, and compositionally valid inferences compared to COMET, CoSe-Co, and baseline PLMs. Additionally, ablation studies confirm that latent graph instantiation significantly improves novelty and coherence metrics, especially under distributional shifts. By bridging the gap between structured reasoning and generative flexibility, AP-LKGI offers a scalable path toward more human-like, adaptive commonsense reasoning systems.",
